        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 text-center">
        <div class="service-box img-rounded">
          <%= image_tag("icon_mainpage_24hr.png") %>
          <h4>24hr到府服務</h4>
          <p class="text-muted">Bananny專門解決臨時到府托育需求，讓寶寶安心待在最熟悉的家中</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-12 text-center">
        <div class="service-box img-rounded">
          <%= image_tag("icon_mainpage_3min.png") %>
